      <description>Hello! Welcome on my website! 😊 Are you puzzled about the name? It is derived from my Chinese name 杨森 (Yáng Sēn). Its close to my real last name Janssen. Frankly, this was a name of an Chinese warlord in Sichuan Province. But I like it!
So why this website? I wanted to create a little space where I can present and gather my project. In the future it may also be the place to reflect on the daily media consume in form of a little blog.</description>
